37856>>>                Case Break
37857>>>
37857>>>            Case Else // must be nfUndefined
37857>>>                // This may be the start of a drilldown query or this may be used for some kind of custom query.
37857>>>
37857>>>        Case End
37857>>>
37857>>>    End_Procedure
